{"tid":451803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"衛詩雅渡海泳挑戰成功：以後過海唔怕塞車","createTime":"2017-10-29T14:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T04:26:29.000Z","uid":156068,"like":132,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"784576b9a78e2cf833acd3e6e3a5c4ed45580709","tid":451803,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"衛詩雅（Michelle）才剛在日本完成電影拍攝，今早（29日)已即趕回香港，與「港隊飛魚」歐鎧淳等暢游維港，最終以25分鐘完成賽事。Michelle完成挑戰後表示:「之前反而成日諗同擔心，但來到現場又突然好冷靜，我在日本拍戲時都有做gym練水，最怕是游錯方向咋。」她又多謝日前阿Sa、柏豪、張繼聰等人拍片為她打氣。「佢哋話得我代表電影界，完成唔到就有啲難睇，搞到我都有少少壓力！」<br />\n<br />\n對於自己用25分鐘完成賽事，Michelle直言感到十分滿意，更指以後不再怕過海塞車，「比我想像中快，雖然我一開始個浮波卡實咗，之後又游錯方向，哈哈！可能因為我同組有港隊的朋友，歐鎧淳及江忞懿等游在我面幫我開路。」Michelle指下年還會再參加，希望可以破個人紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/224408_b9cd691d6ca591c65d31d9b63af6f38f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F224408_b9cd691d6ca591c65d31d9b63af6f38f.jpg&h=c6c19053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/224415_fc2f7dd94c35fc03c400d8aa00da0583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F224415_fc2f7dd94c35fc03c400d8aa00da0583.jpg&h=2bd4f955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5748b65ece55f87e5d9d425d40f094984bb9415d","tid":451803,"uid":7854,"like":218,"dislike":1,"score":217,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://jdailyhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9C%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%94%E5%91%80%E8%88%94%E5%91%80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjdailyhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%2588%2594%25E5%2591%2580%25E8%2588%2594%25E5%2591%2580.jpg&h=aec5d538&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bf34cd06a98a989f49b3ac519822fdddcfe5da8","tid":451803,"uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T15:0